org.apache.hadoop.fs

Interface TestHarFileSystem.MustNotImplement

  • Enclosing class:
    TestHarFileSystem

    private static interface TestHarFileSystem.MustNotImplement
    FileSystem methods that must not be overwritten by HarFileSystem. Either because there is a default implementation already available or because it is not relevant.
